Package: linux-headers-omap
Architecture: armel
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-omap
Description: Linux kernel headers -- omap
 This package will always depend on the latest omap kernel headers
 available.

Package: linux-image-omap
Architecture: armel
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-omap, linux-firmware
Description: Linux kernel image -- omap
 This package will always depend on the latest omap kernel image
 available.

Package: linux-omap
Architecture: armel
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-omap (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Linux kernel -- omap
 This package will always depend on the latest complete omap Linux kernel
 available.

